VPC SECURITY

- Security Groups
	- Firewall at the instance level.
	- Statefull.

- Network access control lists (ACLs)
	- Firewall at the subnet level.
	- Network ACLs as a second layer of defense.
	- Stateless.

- Flow logs
	- Capture information as Cloudwatch logs.